c: 2
v: 173
t: "“Iye akukuletsani (kudya) nyama yofa yokha, liwende, nyama yankhumba ndi nyama yodulidwa poikuwira mayina a mafano kusiya Allah. Koma amene wasimidwa (nadya) popanda kuchikhumba choletsedwacho ndi mosapyoza muyeso palibe tchimo kwa iye. Ndithudi, Allah Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni zedi"